{"word":"Sodom","slug":"sodom","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sodom</b> <a href=\"#/H5467\">H5467</a> <br/> Called also Sodoma.<br/> Situated in the plain of the Jordan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=13&verse=10'>Gen 13:10</a><br/> The southeastern limit of the Canaanites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=19'>Gen 10:19</a><br/> Lot dwells at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=13&verse=12'>Gen 13:12</a><br/> King of, joins other kings of the nations resisting the invasion of Chedorlaomer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=12'>Gen 14:12</a><br/> Wickedness of the inhabitants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=13&verse=13'>Gen 13:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=13'>Gen 19:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=32'>Deu 32:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=9'>Isa 3:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=23&verse=14'>Jer 23:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=4&verse=6'>Lam 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=46'>Eze 16:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=49'>Eze 16:49</a>; <a href='B:'></a><br/> Abraham's intercession for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=33'>Gen 18:33</a><br/> Destroyed on account of the wickedness of the people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=29'>Gen 19:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=29&verse=23'>Deu 29:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=13&verse=19'>Isa 13:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=18'>Jer 49:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=40'>Jer 50:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=4&verse=6'>Lam 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=4&verse=11'>Amo 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=2&verse=9'>Zep 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=15'>Mat 10:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=17&verse=29'>Luk 17:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=9&verse=29'>Rom 9:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=6'>2Pe 2:6</a><br/> Figurative of wickedness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=17'>Deu 23:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=32'>Deu 32:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=1&verse=10'>Isa 1:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=56'>Eze 16:56</a>"}]}